blog.description: Μαυροφορεμένος πάντα με μια κουκούλα και ένα μόνιμο τσιγάρο στο στόμα..

tags: ξεσπαμα διχως λογικη νοημα και τελος
summary: Το κακό είναι, ότι το κακό σχολιάζετε περισσότερο από το καλό.Ακόμα και το "parody" σπανίως βλέπουμε επιτυχίες καλές. Συνήθως...
body:
Το κακό είναι, ότι το κακό σχολιάζετε περισσότερο από το καλό.Ακόμα και το “parody” σπανίως βλέπουμε επιτυχίες καλές. Συνήθως στις αποτυχίες, ίσως γιατί οι “κωμικοί” νιώθουν ασφαλείς στο να μεταφέρουν κάτι που όντως να έχουν επιτυχία μαζεμένη λόγου του περιεχομένου.. χμμμ..

Ένα βήμα πιο μπροστά εγώ.

Δύο εσείς, στάσιμοι στο ίσκιο.

Μία ζωή το ίδιο.

Ο λόγος που δεν μπαίνουν στο μονοπάτι να “κράξουν” μια επιτυχία, δεν είναι επειδή είναι επιτυχία και δεν μπορείς να βρεις κάτι κακό σε αυτό, είναι γιατί πάνε με τον κόσμο.

Εύκολη κριτική, τσεπάκι η νίκη.

Παραδείγματα: youtubers που έγιναν γνωστοί.

Πως έγιναν;

Δεν έχει σημασία τι πιστεύω εγώ,

αλλά τι θέλει ο κόσμος να δει :P

Views, κοινό. Επιτυχία.

Στα αρχίδια μου εγώ.

Και όταν κάνουν κάτι δικό τους, τα views πέφτουν,

και το κοινό που “κέρδισαν” δεν τους βλέπει.

Πούτσες πούτσες πούτσες.

Έως 2015 όλοι κράζανε light, sin boy, snik.

Και ήταν ψηλά οι youtubers.

Φέτος 2019 είναι ψηλά αυτοί.

Και οι συγκεκριμένοι youtubers

τους βλέπει μόνο η μάνα τους.

Μπορείς να το πεις και κάρμα.

Ξέσπασμα δίχως λογική, νόημα και τέλος

-Δαιμεώδης

summary: who/what are some of your favorite youtubers/YouTube channels? (besides you, of course ;P) ~🎷
question: who/what are some of your favorite youtubers/YouTube channels? (besides you, of course ;P) ~🎷
answer:
My channel, obviously ;D

But seriously, I like a bunch of channels. Some of my favorites:

Danny Gonzalez (the Vine Guy) - He does commentary vids on other YouTubers (usually ones with really strange content) and really weird ads and he’s the head of the fastest growing army on the internet (don’t look that up)

Strange Aeons - Lesbian Icon. Also does reaction vids, but mostly on weird Tumblr sub-cultures and things related to the Onion Man (Greg hates her, which tends to be a good sign) @strange-aeons

Ash Hardell - Great videos related to LGBTQ+ topics!! @ashhardell

GenderPunkSap - Another fun LGBTQ+ YouTuber @genderpunksap

PixieLocks - Aesthetic is 10/10 absolutely what I aspire to embody. Jill’s so sweet and she’s living her best rainbow-and-anime-filled life. No cringe culture here. Only rainbows and art and cats and honest approaches to mental health. 

Achievement Hunter - Let’s Plays, mostly. My favorites are their Minecraft videos (they’re up to part 367 now so good luck if you wanted to try and watch them all [I have]), their GTA races/Jack Bags, and their G-mod videos, though I really watch most of their vids. @officialah

Honestly, any of the folks I’m subscribed to on YouTube I subbed to for a reason!

summary: Dating Dan And Phil Would Include
title: Dating Dan And Phil Would Include
body:
Requested by anon:

hey could you write a ‘dating both dan and phil’ would include? i just read the imagine you did about having a relationship with the two of them at the same time and i’d really like to see this! thanks

A/N: This is gonna be pretty vanilla, but also fluffy and cute! :)

  • It’s a huge mess, but in a good kind of way
  • You’re completely spoiled with these two
  • They give you all the cuddles and hugs and kisses
  • And can’t help buying you cute presents
  • Or just things you like, they love spoiling you
  • First and foremost, they’re your best friends
  • So you do everything together and feel comfortable around them
  • You can be yourself with them and the other way around you
  • You play videogames, go out to eat sometimes…
  • All things friends do, hanging out and doing fun stuff
  • But also talk about what’s worrying you and venting
  • Having a shoulder to cry on or just someone to keep you company
  • And it goes the other way around too, you’re there for them as well
  • It’s a very healthy and reciprocal relationship
  • Because you respect and understand each other really well
  • Sometimes they get kinda competitive about you
  • ‘I’m the better boyfriend, Phil!’ ‘No, I love Y/N more!’
  • All in good fun, you know deep down they’re joking
  • And overall they do it to goof around and praise you
  • But that doesn’t mean they don’t ally against you sometimes
  • Especially if you prank them, then the war is on
  • There is a huge amount of teasing, from all three sides
  • Thing is, Dan usually starts the joking insults
  • And then Phil joins in and it’s hilarious
  • Because Phil’s insults are oddly cute and not offensive
  • Using them as pillows all day every day
  • Say, you’re sitting on Dan’s lap but your legs are on Phil’s
  • You’re also their official pillow too, with you in the middle
  • And the two of them hugging you with their head on your shoulders
  • You feel so enveloped and cozy, like two big spoons
  • They both love you a whole lot and plenty of affection ensues
  • Random hugs, compliments, kisses and hand holding
  • Remember the alliances against you? This goes for affection too
  • They will see how much they can embarrass you with compliments
  • Dan especially, he enjoys watching you blush because it’s cute
  • ‘Y/N sandwich’ hugs are a thing, they do happen
  • When you hear any of them say those words you run
  • Because they squash you between them, even if it’s kinda cozy too
  • Having a group text chat with the three of you
  • Full of memes, stupidness and inside jokes
  • Picking each other’s presents together
  • Which also means surprises are planned together as well
  • Mostly Dan and Phil plan things for you
  • Or Dan and you plan things for Phil
  • Dan really doesn’t like surprises
  • Convincing them to actually go outside instead of staying in
  • Even if you love hanging around with them at home
  • Eating pizza, watching anime and cuddling
  • But sometimes you feel like going for a walk and eating outside
  • In general, dating them is the best thing ever

Tag list: @dancewaterdance02, @caswinchester2000​ // If you want me to add you or take you off the tag list, go ahead and tell me!

  • Remember the alliances against you? This goes for affection too
  • They will see how much they can embarrass you with compliments
  • Dan especially, he enjoys watching you blush because it’s cute
  • ‘Y/N sandwich’ hugs are a thing, they do happen
  • When you hear any of them say those words you run
  • Because they squash you between them, even if it’s kinda cozy too
  • Having a group text chat with the three of you
  • Full of memes, stupidness and inside jokes
  • Picking each other’s presents together
  • Which also means surprises are planned together as well
  • Mostly Dan and Phil plan things for you
  • Or Dan and you plan things for Phil
  • Dan really doesn’t like surprises
  • Convincing them to actually go outside instead of staying in
  • Even if you love hanging around with them at home
  • Eating pizza, watching anime and cuddling
  • But sometimes you feel like going for a walk and eating outside
  • In general, dating them is the best thing ever

Tag list: @dancewaterdance02, @caswinchester2000​ // If you want me to add you or take you off the tag list, go ahead and tell me!
